s, debug artifacts, or missing files\n4. If anything fails: one retry via Gemini, then do it yourself\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"91657cad-0549-44af-8ce9-0aa3f1127c9e","uuid":"36e30034-50ff-4139-b657-ff443e3d4cdc","isSynthetic":true}
