. getReviewCount excludes flagged reviews.\n\n5. **src/deps/index.ts** - DependencyGraph implementing DepsService interface. buildTree builds dependency tree using registry.get() to find deps. detectCycles returns arrays of cycle paths (or null if none). topologicalSort returns names in dependency order. flattenDependencies returns all transitive dep names. hasCircularDependency returns boolean.\n\n6. **src/index.ts** - Export createMarketplace() that composes all 5 services. Include installPlugin(manifest) workflow that: validates required fields (name, version, entryPoint), registers plugin, resolves dependency versions, checks for circular deps (reject if found), executes entryPoint in sandbox, returns {resolvedDependencies, executionResult}.\n\nKEY CONSTRAINTS:\n- TypeScript strict mode, ES2022 target, Node16 module system\n- All files must use .ts extension and ESM imports (import/export)\n- Use 'better-sqlite3' for review persistence (in-memory with ':memory:')\n- Use 'semver' package for version operations\n- Use Node.js 'vm' module for sandboxing\n- Modules should only share types from types.ts, not import each other directly\n- Tests go in src/**/*.test.ts files  \n- tsconfig excludes tests dir but vitest still finds .test.ts in src/\n\nWrite comprehensive tests for all modules. Run 'npm run build && npm run lint && npm test'. Fix any failures. Don't stop until all three pass.\" -y 2>&1 | tail -100","description":"Dispatch full implementation to Gemini","timeout":600000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":243,"cache_read_input_tokens":20552,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":243},"output_tokens":26,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"91657cad-0549-44af-8ce9-0aa3f1127c9e","uuid":"57dca358-4fd2-49e8-bac7-919cf7ec146b"}
